  "detailed_description": "<strong>Battle your friends online in a Retro Tank Party!</strong><br><br>It's a wild 2-4 player, top-down tank shooter to keep you trash talking your buddies into the wee hours of the night.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Necessary equipment:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>A broadband internet connection.</strong> This is online <i>only</i>, baby!<br></li><li> <strong>Friends to play with online.</strong> There is matchmaking, but this is a tiny indie game - don't expect to find randos to battle. It's super cheap - buy a couple copies for your friends!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Battle your friends online in a Retro Tank Party!</strong><br><br>It's a wild 2-4 player, top-down tank shooter to keep you trash talking your buddies into the wee hours of the night.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Necessary equipment:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>A broadband internet connection.</strong> This is online <i>only</i>, baby!<br></li><li> <strong>Friends to play with online.</strong> There is matchmaking, but this is a tiny indie game - don't expect to find randos to battle. It's super cheap - buy a couple copies for your friends!</li></ul>",
